thread.title: Shaun Phillips
thread.title_full: Ace Rental Cars Australia & New Zealand reviewed by Shaun Phillips

author: Shaun Phillips
title: Shaun Phillips
text:
The office was busy when we arrived but after a short wait we were given our car. The model ordered was not available so we were upgraded.
The car was a two year old Toyota RAV4 and very clean.
No issues when returning the car either.
